Package control.controller

Class Summary
AcademicStaffController The AcademicStaffController class is a control class that provides operations for academic staff.
AdministratorController AdministratorController class control all the actions that can be perform by the System Admin.
CoordinatorController The CoordinatorController class takes care of all the actions performed by the co-ordinator.
GeneralUserController The GeneralUserController class is a control class that provides operations for general users, which are login/logout, operation of reading profiles of any staffs, and reading details of any publications.
RegisteredUserController The RegisteredUserController class is an abstract class that extends from GeneralUserController.
